1
00:01:03,590 --> 00:01:05,850
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,220 --> 00:01:09,900
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:11,710 --> 00:01:12,560
Who's there?

4
00:01:29,530 --> 00:01:30,590
[Three days ago]

5
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,789
Now that you're here,

6
00:01:32,229 --> 00:01:34,590
have a drink with me.

7
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:37,280
After all,

8
00:01:37,690 --> 00:01:39,890
we're in the same boat.

9
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:45,350
A mighty General

10
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:48,910
drinking to drown
his sorrows over a woman.

11
00:01:48,930 --> 00:01:50,310
How amusing.

12
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:55,200
What brings you here?

13
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,560
Nothing.

14
00:01:58,430 --> 00:02:00,350
I just wanted to see

15
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,950
how pathetic you look.

16
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:18,430
You dare to point your sword at me,

17
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,960
but why don't you

18
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:22,329
dare vent your anger?

19
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,090
What exactly do you want to say?

20
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,360
Jiang Li

21
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,640
was involved with my brother

22
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,750
long before she was engaged to you.

23
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:34,630
She

24
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,590
has been playing you all along.

25
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,570
What did you say?

26
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:42,710
To avoid marrying you, Jiang Li

27
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:46,000
is now hiding with my brother.

28
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:48,030
Probably

29
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,810
they're having a good time.

30
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:54,840
Simo,

31
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,120
I've said all I needed to say.

32
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,840
What you do next

33
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,960
is up to you.

34
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,630
[General's Mansion]

35
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:11,030
Soldiers, heed my command!

36
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,520
Follow me into the palace
to kill that tyrant

37
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,960
for the people!

38
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,800
Yes, sir!

39
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,800
Simo.

40
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,560
Prince Nianzhao,

41
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,430
you've come to see me off?

42
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:37,190
Don't you

43
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:40,590
want revenge?

44
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,710
Revenge?

45
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,120
Now I finally understand.

46
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:46,470
You and your mother
have been using me all along.

47
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,430
If I succeed,

48
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,910
you reap the benefits.

49
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:50,800
If I fail,

50
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,240
I'm just your sacrificial pawn.

51
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,360
Simo, you've misunderstood.

52
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,410
Since things have come to this,

53
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,910
let me tell you a story from the past.

54
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,100
Before your father, the old General Xun,

55
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,710
got married,

56
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,690
he had a childhood sweetheart.

57
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,200
They were deeply in love.

58
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:13,030
This woman came from
the powerful Xuan family

59
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:15,360
and entered the capital
as the Princess Royal's study companion.

60
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,829
She pledged herself to your father.

61
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,390
Chuanmo.

62
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,270
Huaijin.

63
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:29,630
Why are you here?

64
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,730
Getting up so early,

65
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,530
what if you didn't rest well
and disturb the baby?

66
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:38,310
Look at you, all sweaty.

67
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,560
Have you thought of a name?

68
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,830
Tell me.

69
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,690
What do you want to name him?

70
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,360
I'm not good at naming.

71
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,800
What name do you like?

72
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:53,360
But unexpectedly,

73
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:57,240
this woman was favored
by the late Emperor

74
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,080
and selected for the palace.

75
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,390
This legitimate daughter
of the Xuan family

76
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:03,320
was already pregnant with a child.

77
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,390
When she saw the child again,

78
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,600
it was already 8 years later.

79
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:19,390
General Xun Chuanmo arrived
with his family for an audience.

80
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:25,310
[Young Xun Simo]

81
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:28,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

82
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,960
No need for formalities.

83
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,310
So this is Simo?

84
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,000
He must be 8 years old now.

85
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,630
Come and let me have a look.

86
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,430
Go ahead.

87
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,190
Don't be afraid. I...

88
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,310
I'm your aunt.

89
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:04,560
Come to the palace often
to keep me company.

90
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,510
Will you?

91
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,680
Yes.

92
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,950
This is your birthday gift.

93
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,600
I embroidered it myself.

94
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,510
Here, take a look.

95
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,620
Do you like it?

96
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:23,820
[Si]

97
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,750
Yes. Thank you, Aunt.

98
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,000
Thank you,

99
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,430
Yu.

100
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:55,950
Impossible.

101
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,360
You're lying.

102
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,040
You must be lying to me!

103
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,240
If she were truly my mother,

104
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,310
how could she...

105
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:03,270
[Nian]

106
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:05,330
This is Mother's birthday gift to me.

107
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,900
Brother Simo,

108
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,460
don't you understand?

109
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:09,420
[Nian]

110
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:11,180
[Si]

111
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,190
So back then...

112
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,430
She abandoned me.

113
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,360
Mother had no choice

114
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,630
but to give you to her own sister.

115
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,480
She abandoned me!

116
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:29,140
I always thought
my mother treated me poorly

117
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:31,070
because I wasn't good enough.

118
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:33,510
I desperately tried to prove myself,

119
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:36,000
but she never wanted
to hear a word from me.

120
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:37,950
Turns out...

121
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,430
I'm not her biological son.

122
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:44,950
I'm just an unwanted bastard.

123
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,070
Do you want Mother

124
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:48,070
to face the crime of clan extermination?

125
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,490
Brother Simo,

126
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,190
we are half-brothers with the same mother.

127
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:54,190
If Mother didn't care about you,

128
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:56,360
why would she risk having me save you?

129
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,159
What did you say?

130
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,040
This is as far as I can help you.

131
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,390
Once you're out,

132
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:06,040
you know what to do.

133
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,270
Brother.

134
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,600
We agreed from the beginning

135
00:08:35,909 --> 00:08:39,640
not to ask about each other's past,
only to enjoy our time together.

136
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,030
Report!

137
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,600
Your Majesty,

138
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,320
Xun Simo has escaped.

139
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:52,750
When did this happen?

140
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,720
Last night.

141
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,870
All five guards on duty were killed.

142
00:08:55,870 --> 00:08:57,270
So the exact circumstances

143
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,670
may be hard to determine.

144
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,550
Take men to Chunliu Garden at once

145
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:01,680
to protect Jiang Li!

146
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:02,790
Forgive my bluntness,

147
00:09:02,790 --> 00:09:04,670
but I should be guarding
Your Majesty right now.

148
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:06,200
You are the only one I trust.

149
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,180
Yes, Your Majesty.

150
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,750
I warned you before, Mother,

151
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,320
that it was the last time.

152
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,510
I never thought you'd be so stubborn,

153
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,960
secretly releasing the criminal Xun Simo.

154
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:38,720
What are you talking about?

155
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,180
I don't understand what you mean.

156
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:45,840
Who else could
sneak into the palace at night

157
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,480
and take Xun Simo away

158
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,960
if not you, Mother?

159
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,670
If Your Majesty believes I did it,

160
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,720
then so be it.

161
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:02,870
Are you really

162
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,150
going to kill

163
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:09,390
your own mother?

164
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,000
You...

165
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,150
Guards!

166
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:20,840
Yes!

167
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,080
By my decree,

168
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,630
from this day forth,

169
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,750
the Empress Dowager and her attendants
are confined to her palace.

170
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,810
They're not allowed to step outside.

171
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,840
Those who disobey will be executed!

172
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:32,750
Yes, Your Majesty.
